title: Kyle Christie on Fatherhood and the ‘Spies, Lies, and Allies’ Final | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Kyle Christie makes his illustrious return to the podcast to talk to Johnny about his newfound fatherhood, the final of ‘Spies, Lies, and Allies,’ and much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Kyle Christie
